  "title": "Modern Security Strategy",
  "contentHtml": "In this episode Michael and Mark talk with Microsoft Security MVP Truls Dahlsveen&nbsp;\n                  (\n                     <a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer\" href='https://www.linkedin.com/in/truls-dahlsveen/?originalSubdomain=no'><i class=\"fa-brands fa-linkedin\"></i></a>\n                  ) \n                  about modern security strategy. Actually, Mark and Truls mainly do the talking :)\n\n                  <br>\n                  We also discuss Azure Security news about Application Gateway TLS policy, Defender for IoT and the Zero Trust Commandments.\n\n                  <br><br>\n\n                  <!-- Insert episode info from rss.com into NNNNNN and TTTTTT which is the episode number and the title -->\n                  <iframe loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://player.rss.com/azsecpodcast/1064208?theme=light\" class=\"podcast-player\" title=\"The Azure Security Podcast\" frameborder=\"0\"><a href=\"https://rss.com/podcasts/azsecpodcast/1064208/\">TTTTTTT</a></iframe>\n\n                  <h5>Links</h5> \n                  <!-- Links to transcription and news articles -->\n                  <ul>\n                     <li><a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer\" href='https://rss.com/podcasts/azsecpodcast/1064208/'>Transcript <i class=\"fa-solid fa-book\"></i></a></li>\n\n                     <li><a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer\" href=\"https://pubs.opengroup.org/security/zero-trust-commandments/snapshot/\">Zero Trust Commandments</a></li>\n                     <li><a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer\" href=\"https://azure.microsoft.com/en-us/updates/default-tls-policy-2022/\">Updated default TLS policy for Azure Application Gateway</a></li>\n                     <li><a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer\" href=\"https://azure.microsoft.com/en-us/updates/public-preview-firmware-analysis-in-defender-for-iot/\">Public Preview: Firmware analysis in Defender for IoT </a></li>\n                     <li><a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer\" href=\"https://azure.microsoft.com/en-us/updates/preview-azure-boost/\">Preview: Azure Boost</a></li>\n\n                     <li><a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer\" href=\"https://www.infernux.no/\">Truls' Security Automation Blog</a></li>\n                     <li><a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer\" href=\"https://www.infernux.no/SecurityStrategy/\">Field notes on security strategy</a></li>\n                     <li><a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer\" href=\"https://www.youtube.com/@microsoftsecurityinsights\">Microsoft Security Insights</a></li>\n                     <li><a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer\" href=\"https://www.youtube.com/@msems\">Microsoft EMS Community</a></li>\n\n                  </ul>"
